snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Amma Aligithey || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Amma Aligithey || MCM

In this new Middle Class Madhu episode, the video opens with the game we all used to play as kids, Allilu Aata (Game With Marbles). Our Naatu Guntalu Gang returns home after enjoying a good time. Madhu returns home and discovers no food, which makes him angry with his mother. In the meantime, after a busy day at work Madhus' father arrives home and discovers no excellent food, which makes him angry with his wife. Even though Madhu's mother does all the housework to the best of her ability, she feels horrible because of Madhu and his husband. For an entertaining twenty minute journey, watch the complete video of this Amma Aligithey episode, "What if mom gets angry?"

snippet.title: White Brown Black - Avvy Sra | Karan Aujla | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
The most awaited collaboration of the year is finally here, Avvy Sra and Karan Aujla join hands to deliver ‘White Brown Black.' Everything about this song is the gold standard from Karan’s ace rap to Jaani’s unforgettable writing and Avvy’s impeccable music production. ‘White Brown Black’ goes hard with its modern sound design combined with folk elements; making it an absolute banger. The music video directed by Amaninder Singh from Arvindr Khaira’s team is everything you needed to complement Avvy and Karan’s fire vocals.

Listen to 'White Brown Black' on your favourite streaming platform - UMGI.lnk.to/WBB

Singer - Avvy Sra 
Rap - Karan Aujla
Music - Avvy Sra
Composer - Jaani
Lyricist - Jaani, Karan Aujla
Featuring - Gagan Sahi
Mix & Master - Jaydden

Director - Amanninder Singh
DOP - Sukha Kamboj 
Assistant Director - Akarsh Tiwana
Editing - Zipsi (Zipsi Studio)

Stylist - Jyoti Singh

Brand Integration - Net Media

https://www.instagram.com/desimelodies/

Oh shoe Versace jatta de kake kanni waaliyan ni
Babbar sher ae full daler ae
7 denaliyan ni….. x 2

3 shaunk ne patt honiye jatt de munde de x 2

Ghodde chitte, kudiyan brown, gaddiya kaaliyan ni…. x 2

Oh shoe Versace jatta de kake kanni waaliyan ni
Babbar sher ae full daler ae 
7 denaliyan ni…..

Oh Ghodde chitte, kudiyan brown, gaddiya kaaliyan ni….

Jattan di hikka ch zor
Louis ton leke Dior
Gallan na sari tu gerha tan mari tu 
Yaaran kolo hundi ni bore
Dinda kithe chance hunda goriyan de dance 
Baby on my phone je tu krna romance
Feel kre shy aa le shart lagayi
Meri akhan vich dekh tenu krdange high

Ni 2 vich kothi khanda motti
Yaar ne pakke assi ni rakhe
Chamche thaaliyan ni…..

Ghodde chitte, kudiyan brown, gaddiya kaaliyan ni…. x 2

Kise ton patteya jana ni teesi da berr aa goriye 
Je duniya teri jungle aa fer jatt sher aa goriye

Kise da darr na 
Koka jadd’na
Kathe hoge JAANI te KARNA 
Roz diwaliyan ni

3 shaunk ne patt honiye jatt de munde de X 2
Ghodde chitte, kudiyan brown, gaddiya kaaliyan ni…. x 3

snippet.description:
#mainpuribyelection  #akhileshyadav   #shivpalyadav 

Mainpuri Bypoll Election Result: Samajwadi Party संस्थापक Mulayam Singh Yadav के निधन से खाली हुई Mainpuri लोकसभा सीट पर हुए उपचुनाव के बाद वोटों की गिनती में Akhilesh Yadav की पत्नी Dimple Yadav ने बंपर जीत हासिल की है. वहीं Mainpuri में Dimple की जीत के बाद Shivpal Singh Yadav की पार्टी प्रसपा का Samajwadi Party में विलय हो गया है. snippet.title: Match Highlights - Portugal 6:1 Switzerland - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
No Cristiano Ronaldo, no problem as Portugal crushed Switzerland 6-1 to reach the #FIFAWorldCup quarter-finals for the first time since 2006.

Goncalo Ramos was the star performer in #PORSUI as he netted a sensational hat-trick; the first of #Qatar2022. Pepe & Raphael Guerreiro also got their names on the scoresheet in between the Benfica striker's goals. Substitute Rafael Leao added the cherry on top of the icing with a sublime finish in injury time.

Manuel Akanji bagged the consolation for Switzerland.

Enjoy the highlights of this clash & remember to watch Portugal in action again on Dec 10 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

Goncalo Ramos was the star performer in #PORSUI as he netted a sensational hat-trick; the first of #Qatar2022. Pepe & Raphael Guerreiro also got their names on the scoresheet in between the Benfica striker's goals. Substitute Rafael Leao added the cherry on top of the icing with a sublime finish in injury time.

Manuel Akanji bagged the consolation for Switzerland.

Enjoy the highlights of this clash & remember to watch Portugal in action again on Dec 10 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain.

snippet.description:
#HimachalElectionResult    #reenakashyap     #LiveHindustan

Himachal Election में कांग्रेस पार्टी ने 40 सीटों के साथ बहुमत का आंकड़ा पार कर लिया है. इस बार चुनाव में कई ऐसे रिकॉर्ड बने जिसकी उम्मीद नहीं थी. चलिए आपको एक ऐसे ही हटकर खबर दिखाते है. और वो खबर है कि इस बार एक मात्र महिला विधायक विधानसभा पहुंची है. आखिर कौन. आपके मन में ये सवाल आ रहा होगा. तो चलिए बताते है. 68 सदस्यीय हिमाचल विधानसभा में पहुंचने वाली एकमात्र महिला विधायक कौन हैं..

snippet.title: Decorating Home for Christmas in Tamil | Christmas Shopping Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video join me during the christmas shopping and decorating the home during the festival season. It is always fun to decorate the home during christmas and putting up the christmas tree. I had also collected a lot of ornaments during the new years and its always bring joy to put them up. We also decorated the yard with some holiday lights and candy canes. We  also visited a couple of shops to take a look at the new decorations this year.

snippet.title: Kyaa Baat Haii 2.0 | Govinda Naam Mera | Vicky, Kiara | Harrdy, Tanishk, Nikhita, Jaani, B Praak
snippet.description:
A song that is “bound” to leave you hitting the rewind button again and again, “Kyaa Baat Haii 2.0” features Vicky Kaushal and Kiara Advani from Govinda Naam Mera. Composed by B Praak and recreated by Tanishk Bagchi, it is written by Jaani. Sung by Harrdy Sandhu and Nikhita Gandhi, watch till the end for a surprise twist!

#KyaaBaatHaii2 #GovindaNaamMera #VickyKaushal #KiaraAdvani #BPraak #HarrdySandhu #TanishkBagchi #Jaani #NikhitaGandhi

Recreated by: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyrics: Jaani
Singers: Harrdy Sandhu and Nikhita Gandhi
Music Supervisor - Azeem Dayani
Mixed and mastered by: Eric Pillai
Programming and arrangement by: Tanishk Bagchi
Choreographer - Tushar Kalia
Special thanks - Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Online Promotion: Net Media

KYA BAAT AY ORIGINAL SONG CREDITS
Lyrics and composition: Jaani
Music: B Praak
Singer: Harrdy Sandhu
Mixed and mastered by: Eric Pillai

Lyrics:
Tera mukhda chand da tukda 
Ni teri ainak, tere shoe
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
[music]
Kyaa baat haii
Mujhko tere ye ishaare samaj nahi aate 
Lekin dil ne sun li hai teri dil waali baatein, 
Mujhko tere ye ishaare samaj nahi aate 
Lekin dil ne sun li hai teri dil waali baatein; 
Tere lakk ton tu lagda Karachi di 
Fan marjaniye Bugatti di
Dil kare tere naal banneyaa ravaan 
Tere jism’ch khushboo elachi di 
Ni tera kajal
Karda ae pagal 
Hypnotize kare jatt nu 
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
Meri akh, te teekha nakk 
Uspe yeh mashallah muhn 
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
[music] 
Mera Kangana Kangana Kangana 
Kyaa baat haii
Lagg ni pai
Pai mein baddi hot marjaneya
Menu takk ke tenu aande gande thought marjaneya 
Lagg ni paiyaan
Paiyaan badi hot marrjaniye 
Tenu takk ke mennu
Aande gande thought marjaniye 
Gallan ne gulabi vich toye nakhro 
Karde ne munde hoye hoye nakhro 
Jedha tennu takk lava ikk vaar ni 
Tin - char mahine to’na soye nakhro 
Teri chaal te gallan laal 
Te saari di saari hi tu 
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
[music] 
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
Jaani...jaani... jaani jaani jaani 
Jaani nu tu aa gayi pasand baliye 
Tapne nu fire teri kandh baliye
Mennu seene naal la le 
Naa keh No!! No!! No!!
Tere bina menu maar di ay thand baliye 
Tera mukhda chand da tukda 
Ni teri ainak, tere shoe
Kyaa baat haii
Kyaa baat haii
[music]
Kyaa baat haii
[music]
Kyaa baat haii

snippet.title: Isudan Gadhvi એ ખંભાળિયાથી હાર બાદ પોતાના રાજકીય ભવિષ્ય વિશે શું કહ્યું? Gujarat Election 2022
snippet.description:
#aapgujarat #isudangadhvi #gujaratelection2022 #gujaratinews #gujaratelectionresult 

ગુજરાત વિધાનસભા ચૂંટણીમાં આમ આદમી પાર્ટીના મુખ્ય મંત્રીપદના ચહેરા ઈસુદાન ગઢવી ખંભાળિયાની બેઠક પરથી ચૂંટણી હારી ગયા છે. હાર બાદ અમે તેમની પ્રતિક્રિયા જાણવા તેમની સાથે વાતચીત કરી અને આગળ તેમની રાજનૈતિક દિશા શું રહેશે તેઓ  તેમના મતવિસ્તાર અને પક્ષ માટે કયા કાર્યોનું લક્ષ્ય રાખે છે એ જાણવાનો પ્રયાસ કર્યો.
તેમની સાથે વાતચીત કરી બીબીસી સહયોગી હનીફ ખોખરે.


વીડિયો- હનીફ ખોખર/ સુમિત વૈદ્ય

તમે અમારી સાથે જોડાઈ શકો છો :

snippet.title: The Search For Coconuts Begins | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Watch the best moment from your beloved show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah where are characters are here to take you on a joyous ride. Get on the happy train and enjoy how these characters navigate through their daily lives in a hilarious way! Jethalal, Taarak, and all of the members eagerly await you.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1393
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #SonyPAL

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G0GGKekdfESeKWx2JOF9NFL

snippet.title: श्री कृष्ण लीला | श्री कृष्ण ने अश्वत्थामा को दिया था श्राप
snippet.description:
भक्त को भगवान से और जिज्ञासु को ज्ञान से जोड़ने वाला एक अनोखा अनुभव। तिलक प्रस्तुत करते हैं दिव्य भूमि भारत के प्रसिद्ध धार्मिक स्थानों के अलौकिक दर्शन। दिव्य स्थलों की तीर्थ यात्रा और संपूर्ण भागवत दर्शन का आनंद। 

Watch the video song of ''Darshan Do Bhagwaan'' here - https://youtu.be/j7EQePGkak0

Watch the story of "Shree krshn ne ashvatthaama ko diya tha shraap" now!

Watch Janmashtami Special Krishna Bhajan - Govind Madhav Jai Jai Gopal by Dev Negi - http://bit.ly/GovindMadhavJaiJaiGopal

अश्वत्थामा ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को पांडवों पर छोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण अर्जुन को कहते हैं की तुम भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र का प्रयोग कर अश्वत्थामा के अस्त्र को रोकने के लिए कहते हैं। अर्जुन भी अपने ब्रह्मषिर अस्त्र को चला देता है। वेदव्यास जी दोनों अस्त्रों के बीच में आकर उन्हें आपस में टकराने से रोक देते हैं और दोनों को अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेने के लिए कहते हैं अर्जुन उनकी बात मान कर अपना अस्त्र वापस ले लेता है। लेकिन जब अश्वत्थामा उन्हें कहता है की मैं इस अस्त्र को वापस लेने की विद्या नहीं जानता। वेदव्यास जी अश्वत्थामा को कहते हैं की तुम इसे यदि वापस नहीं ले सकते तो तुम इसे पृथ्वी के उस हिस्से पर मोड़ दो जहां कोई भी जीव नहीं है और इसके बदले में तुम्हें पांडवों से अभय दान दिलवाता हूँ। श्री कृष्ण पांडवों से अश्वत्थामा को अभ्यदान देने के बदले उसकी दिव्य मणि को माँगते हैं जो की उसे सिर के भीतर थी जिस से उसे ना कभी भूक लगती थी और वह राज मुक्त रहता था। अश्वत्थामा अपने ब्रह्मषिर अभिमनयु की पत्नी उत्तरा के गर्भ की ओर मोड़ देता है। श्री कृष्ण उत्तरा के गर्भ की रक्षा करने के लिए अपने सुदर्शन चक्र को भेजते हैं। श्री कृष्ण ब्रह्मा जी से कहते हैं की आप अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लें क्योंकि अश्वत्थामा ने इसका प्रयोग ग़लत कार्य के लिए किया है। ब्रह्मा जी अपने अस्त्र को वापस ले लेते हैं। श्री कृष्ण अश्वत्थामा को अपने कर्म के कारण श्राप देते हैं की तुम हज़ारों वर्षों के लिए इसी कल में जीवित रहोगे तुम्हें मृत्युु नहीं आएगी और तुमसे कोई भी इंसान बात नहीं करेगा और तुम्हारा शरीर ऐसा हो जाएगा की तुम स्वयं अपनी शक्ल को देख कर भी डर जाओगे। श्री कृष्ण भीम को अश्वत्थामा की दिव्य मणि निकल कर लाने के लिए कहते हैं। भीम उस मणि को उसके सर से निकल लेता है।

श्री कृष्ण के सभी एपिसोड और भजन देखने के लिए Subscribe करें तिलक YouTube चैनल को। 

Subscribe to Tilak for more devotional contents - https://bit.ly/SubscribeTilak

श्रीकृष्णा, रामानंद सागर द्वारा निर्देशित एक भारतीय टेलीविजन धारावाहिक है। मूल रूप से इस श्रृंखला का दूरदर्शन पर साप्ताहिक प्रसारण किया जाता था। यह धारावाहिक कृष्ण के जीवन से सम्बंधित कहानियों पर आधारित है। गर्ग संहिता , पद्म पुराण , ब्रह्मवैवर्त पुराण अग्नि पुराण, हरिवंश पुराण , महाभारत , भागवत पुराण , भगवद्गीता आदि पर बना धारावाहिक है सीरियल की पटकथा, स्क्रिप्ट एवं काव्य में बड़ौदा के महाराजा सयाजीराव विश्वविद्यालय के हिन्दी विभाग के अध्यक्ष डॉ विष्णु विराट जी ने महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका निभाई। इसे सर्वप्रथम दूरदर्शन के मेट्रो चैनल पर प्रसारित 1993 को किया गया था जो 1996 तक चला, 221 एपिसोड का यह धारावाहिक बाद में दूरदर्शन के डीडी नेशनल पर टेलीकास्ट हुआ, रामायण व महाभारत के बाद इसने टी आर पी के मामले में इसने दोनों धारावाहिकों को पीछे छोड़ दिया था,इसका पुनः जनता की मांग पर प्रसारण कोरोना महामारी 2020 में लॉकडाउन के दौरान रामायण श्रृंखला समाप्त होने के बाद ०३ मई से डीडी नेशनल पर किया जा रहा है, TRP के मामले में २१ वें हफ्ते तक यह सीरियल नम्बर १ पर कायम रहा।

snippet.title: Thee Thalapathy | Thalapathy Vijay | Varisu | STR | Vamshi Paidipally | Thaman
snippet.description:
Here is the most awaited second single "Thee Thalapathy" lyric video of Thalapathy Vijay’s #Varisu. 

Film Credits: 

Director: Vamshi Paidipally Producer: Raju, Shirish 
Banner: Sri Venkateswara Creations 
Co:Producers: Sri Harshith Reddy, Sri Harshitha Composed by Thaman S 

Star Cast: Vijay, Rashmika Mandanna, R Sarathkumar, Prabhu, Prakash Raj, Shaam, Srikanth, Khushbu, Yogi Babu, Jayasudha, Sangeetha Krish, Samyuktha Shanmughanathan, Nandini Rai, Ganesh Venkatraman, Sriman, VT Ganesan, John Vijay, Bharath Reddy, Sanjana and others.

Lyrics: Vivek 

Musician Credits: 
Arranged & Programmed by Thaman S 
Live Lead Drums: Thaman S

Electric Guitar: Godfrey

Prudhvi Chandra & Saicharan

New edge ( Mumbai ) & New Edge ( NY ) 
Assistant by Pukraj & Anup 
Musician coordinator: Manikandan K 
Studio Manger: Seenu & Sridhar 
Studio Assistance: Kannan Lingam Raju & Ranjith 


Lyrics: 
Unna paathu sirichaa 
Adha ullukkulla nerupaakku 
Avamaanam kedachaa 
adhil greedam onna uruvaakku 
Unna kuththi ulagame 
aanandham adayume 
Thiruppi adikkum bodhu dhaan yaaru neennu puriyume 
Its time its time to give it:u back:u maame 
Idhu thiruppi idhu thiruppi kudukkum neram maame 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi 
Stanza 
Kaayam poruthu Sendru pazhagu mul irukkum vazhiyile 
Kooda nadandha kootta satham pullarikkum udalile 
Kaalgal thadukki malayil irundhu keezhe pogum nodiyile 
Kaigal asaithu paaru pudhiya rekkai pirakkum vazhiyile 
Kanneero 
Nee unakku sollum aaraaro 
Kan thoongi ezhundha pinbu nee vero 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi

snippet.title: Mainpuri की जीत पर Dimple को CM Yogi ने दी बधाई, Rampur में पहली बार मिली जीत पर कही बड़ी बात
snippet.description:
#mainpuribyelection  #cmyogi  #dimpleyadav 

UP Bypolls Results 2022: उत्तर प्रदेश में Mainpuri, Rampur और Khatauli की सीट पर उपचुनाव के नतीजे सामने आ गए हैं. रामपुर में बीजेपी और खतौली में सपा गठबंधन को जीत हासिल हुई है. वहीं Mainpuri लोकसभा सीट पर सपा की Dimple Yadav ने बड़े मार्जन से बीजेपी प्रत्याशी Raghuraj Singh Shakya को धूल चटा दी. उपचुनाव के नतीजे सामने आने के बाद प्रदेश के CM Yogi Adityanath ने डिंपल यादव को मैनपुरी सीट पर जीत की बधाई दी. साथ ही सीएम ने खतौली और रामपुर के विजेता प्रत्याशियों को भी जीत की शुभकामनाएं दी.

snippet.description:
Find peace, quiet and love in the tunes of #SanjayLeelaBhansali's first-ever original music album #Sukoon!

Buy Carvaan Mobile- Feature phone with 1500 Pre-loaded songs at http://sarega.ma/ycmbuy

Makeup: Sushil Kumar Swami
Stylists : Pranav Sood & Krisna Krishnankutty

Lyrics:

Mukhda
Ishq Teri Ankhon Mein Likha
Padhne De Zara
Hum Ko Bhi Ghalib Hona Hai
In Ghazlon Si Ankhon Mein Khona Hai

1st Antara
Ghazlen Hum Tujh Pe Likhte Rahen
Shayar Ban Ban Ke Ugte Rahen.
Tera Chehera Koi Kitab Sa Hai
Tera Milna Koi Khwab Sa Hai
Iss Khwab Mein Khud Ko Dubona Hai

2nd Antara
Tere Hothon Se Sher Barasten Hain
Hum Baton Ko Teri Taraste Hain
Tera Hum Se Kalam Jo Ho Jaye
To Hamara Naam Bhi Ho Jaye
Teri Palkon Mein Khud Ko Perona Hai

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3637 - 9 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3637
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal meets Vidya and then heads back to Gokhuldham. Bhide inquires about Popatlal's whereabouts because he has been absent from society. Popatlal tells Bhide that he was busy with a sting operation. Later, Bhide's uncle Sudhakar Ji calls him, and he sounds furious since he observed Popatlal meeting Vidya covertly. Bhide is shocked to learn that Popatlal had visited the village and met Vidya. He is puzzled and attempts to understand how Popatlal learned the location of the village and Vidya. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3637, 9 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000198787

snippet.title: JAISA DES WAISA BHES | Ft. Chhavi Mittal, Shubhangi & Aarti | Hindi Comedy Short Film | SIT
snippet.description:
Being loved, being accepted, and looking good are everybody’s desires, but sometimes we cross all boundaries to fulfil this desire of ours. When Kaamwali Bai, aka Baby, and Mrs. Verma do the same, Rohini is in a soup. In this comedy short film, you will see how Rohini makes them understand that self-acceptance is the first step to finding love and also being loved. Watch this super fun short film, "Jaisa Des Waisa Bhes," streaming only on the Shitty Ideas Trending YouTube channel.

#Comedy #ComedyShortFilm #IndianComedy #SIT

ABOUT SIT:
Shitty Ideas Trending creates light-hearted, fun videos based on everyday situations. Husband wife comedy sketches, Web Series, relationship banter, couple humour and meaningful fictional short films. Whether you are glued to watching the cute and adorable husband Rishi with his wife Rohini, or the smart and suave Abhimanyu with his wife Meera, whether you love to watch the adorable yet eccentric maid Baby or are just addicted to little Jahaan’s smile, or maybe you like to get a dose of relationship tips from Abhimanyu or just want to avoid the mistakes that Rishi makes, SIT is the place for everybody who wishes to get a dose of entertainment when on the move. The videos are short and snackable and are for one and all. Ranging from THE BETTER HALF with Chhavi Mittal and Karan V Grover, PYAR KA PUNCH with Pracheen Chauhan and Pooja Gor, MAID IN HEAVEN with Shubhangi Litoria, or GRASS IS GREENER ON THE OTHER SIDE with a combination of Chhavi Mittal, Karan V Grover, Pracheen Chauhan, Pooja Gor, creator MOHIT HUSSEIN brings you a great mix of content.

Lyrics -

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori tedhi tedhi taak ke,
Likdi saare mauke naap ke,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran dar ja kade ram te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Nakhro, dekha pahli dafa,
College ke bahar dass kya thi raza,
Chale left to right bata kyu di saza,
Louis, LV tight teri kaidi ada,
Chhore paache paache haande leke landi jeep,
Tere chakkar me kare kaand galt hi cheej,
Gere 5 inch heel, Chhore leve poori feel,
Tere bhaav bhi to fly kare poori dheel,

Makke tip to toe tu poori gach hai,
26 ki kamar poori lachke,
21 ki umar, kya ye sach hai?
Mere bethi hai nishaane pe rah bachke,

Halla mach gaya poore gaam me,
Ib bethak laage shaam ne,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Beran darja kadi raam te,

Chhori Ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani,

Tu hoga badmaash tere laake me chhore,
Tere jaise pade fail mere khaate me chhore,
Manne Jhaanse me laane ki koshish na kar,
Maanja padega ghane ghaate me chhore,

Teri chikni chupdi baat me,
Chhori aati koni saath me,
Chhora ke khanjar ghaal ke,
Kyunkar darjua raam te,

Haan me ghani syaani ghani syaani ghani syaani,
Chhore mar gaye mar gaye mar gaye haan bin maange paani


#GhaniSyaani #MCSquare #ShehnaazGill

About MaaTri Media

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand.

MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain. 

Watch our videos every Thursday & learn new dishes and kitchen hacks or food hacks with us as we entertain you with our comical presentation.

snippet.title: சுத்தம் தான் முக்கியம் 🤩 | Our Cleaning Routine 🧹 | Shrutika Arjun
snippet.description:
Safewash is Wipro’s liquid detergent brand. Safewash Safewash's color protect technology & acid free formula ensures clothes look new even after 75+ washes but is also good for washing machine. Safewash liquid detergent dissolves completely in water while powder detergent leaves a lot of filler residue.  Safewash gets filtered easily without any residue keeping your clothes and machine healthy and happy.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3636 - 8 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3636
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal is at the school when he meets a peon who asks him about Vidya. Popatlal waits for Vidya's lectures to be over on the school's grounds. He then goes and meets Vidya who then learns that he is not a teacher but a journalist. Vidya first thinks that he is here for an interview and is more than happy to give one. However, when the truth comes out she refuses to talk about marriage to him and asks him to talk to her dad. Popatlal gives Vidya her number and her dad asks her who he is. He sees the card and is angry. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3636, 8 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000198597

snippet.title: Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Ep. 555 | Sankar Threatens Neha | शंकर ने नेहा को दी धमकी
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Bihaan refuses to take help from Thapki and promises to win against Kabir. Meanwhile, Sankar plans to take revenge on Thapki and threatens Neha to kill her.

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Neha lays a trap to get rid of Thapki by using the power of black magic. She takes Sankar's help to execute the plan. Will Thapki fall victim to this ploy? Elsewhere, Kabir insults Bihaan and stops him from taking loans from outsiders.

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

An epic battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.

- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. - A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile

- New events and game modes daily

- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins

- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

Features:
- Team up for real-time 3v3 battles against players from across the world
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile
- Unlock and collect new, powerful Brawlers - each with a signature attack and Super ability
- New events and game modes daily
- Battle solo or with friends
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings 
- Join or start your own Club with fellow players to share tips and battle together
- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins
- Player-designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master

From the makers of Clash of Clans, Clash Royale and Boom Beach!

Siyani Episode 116 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 8th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Noor Bhai Ki Purani Aashiqui Part 2 || 90's Ki Love Story || Shehbaaz Khan & Team
snippet.description:
Hello Everyone!
We are back with the sequel of “Noor Bhai Ki Purani Ashiqui” 😍❤️. Yes! You heard that right 🤩 the tragedy is not over yet!
I know you guys watched the Part-1 of “Noor Bhai ki Ashiqui” and showed so much love and support, I really appreciate that 🤗❤️.
And on a huge public demand we are back with Part-2 and this video is loaded with lots of Comedy, Drama, love, and suspense….😍
So, What happened next after Noor Bhai’s love “Zubeda” leaves him alone by calling her brother and her son as Mamu. Then after Noor Bhai gets traumatized and depressed thinking about it. The other people also feel sorrow for “Noor Bhai” and one of his friend says “Noor bhai” to just forget her and abuse her for breaking his heart 💔. Noor bhai gets angry and slaps him for abusing her in front of him and tells him how much he loves her.
After time passes… “Noor Bhai” and his friend are busy doing some work then suddenly his Love “Zubeda” approaches….. What did they discuss??? That’s the suspense you should watch the full video to know.
And if you really liked the video, please share it with your family and friends.
Thanks a lot for supporting us always ❤️.

#aashiqui #noorbhai #comedy 

Artists - Shehbaaz Khan, Saba Khan, Sameera Princess, Amer Bin Sayeed
Atif Khan, Salman Shaik, Lateef Prince.

snippet.title: ഇന്നോവ ക്രിസ്റ്റയുടെ പിൻഗാമിയാണ് സ്ട്രോങ്ങ് ഹൈബ്രിഡ് ഹൃദയമുള്ള ഹൈക്രോസ്സ് | Toyota  Innova Hycross
snippet.description:
ടൊയോട്ട ഇന്നോവ ക്രിസ്റ്റയുടെ അടുത്ത തലമുറക്കാനായി രംഗത്തെത്തിയിരിക്കുകയാണ് ഇന്നോവ ഹൈക്രോസ്സ്.പെട്രോൾ-ഇലക്ട്രിക്ക് മോട്ടോർ സെറ്റപ്പുള്ള ഹൈക്രോസിന് കമ്പനി പറയുന്ന മൈലേജ് 21 കിലോമീറ്ററാണ്...

ആയിരക്കണക്കിന് പുസ്തകങ്ങൾ ഇനി ദിവസവും 1 രൂപയിൽ താഴെ ചിലവിൽ വർഷം മുഴുവനും കേട്ട് അറിയൂ.
Download India's no 1 audio book platform: 
https://kukufm.page.link/sTEFGRUtEW4Ej6XS8

snippet.title: 2022 Toyota Innova Hycross review - India's favourite MPV reborn | First Drive | Autocar India
snippet.description:
The all-new Toyota Innova Hycross is an Innova unlike any before. It makes the radical switch to a monocoque construction and front-wheel drive layout, and it's only on sale with petrol and petrol strong hybrid options. And there's a greater focus on luxury. Gavin D'Souza tells you how it all comes together. 

Cameraperson: Mritunjay Chakarborty
Editor: Mohit Sharma
